item.title: SCKRK - 100 meetings, 96 whitepapers, 5 years and more...
item.description:
This post was originally written on 16 May 2016.

Over the last years I’ve been had the privilege of traveling quite a bit and been able to attend various conferences and user group meetings in various countries. Yet, I’m still to find another as awesome and life-changing (sic, not an over-statement) group as SCKRK â€“ yet, you’ve probably never heard of it. Which is not surprising really since it’s a local and technically speaking small initiative.
